 - exlib/hep/polyhedron : use memcpy to copy G4Facet.
 - to wall : send bsg buffers.
 - to wall : correct mem leak in exlib/sg/sf_polyhedron
 - Cocoa : menubar/Quit -> clear tmp.

 - for iOS : change the unfolding of res zip file so that they go in
   the tmp dir. The AppleStore does not want more than 6 Mbytes of
   data in the doc dir coming from the app.
 - scene popup : center.
 - h_zz_4mu.cmnd, h_gamma_gamma.cmnd : switch off dumps.
 - files : .cmnd : it sets geant4::primary_generator.
 - pythia8 : correct ParticleData::nextId(). See //G.Barrand comment.
   Seen when porting to WIN32.

